- **Single conversation dragging** from native Gemini sidebar into folders
- **Multi-select dragging** (long-press to enter multi-select mode, then drag multiple conversations)
- **Folder dragging** (move folders between parent folders and to/from root level)
- **Reordering** (conversations and folders can be reordered within same parent)
- **Cross-folder moving** (conversations can move between folders)

**Two implementations exist:**
1. **`src/pages/content/folder/manager.ts`** - For Google Gemini (gemini.google.com)
2. **`src/pages/content/folder/aistudio.ts`** - For Google AI Studio (aistudio.google.com/prompts)

