### 5. EVENT HANDLERS IN DETAIL

#### A. **dragstart** (Making things draggable)

**Conversations:** `manager.ts` lines 1471-1551
```typescript
element.addEventListener('dragstart', (e) => {
  // Check if multiple selections exist
  if (this.selectedConversations.size > 1) {
    // Multi-select drag - includes all selected
    const dragData: DragData = {
      type: 'conversation',
      title: `${selectedConvs.length} conversations`,
      conversations: selectedConvs,
    };
